                                    % if ctx['joined_ids']:
                                        Work From Home option has been facilitated to ${ctx['joined_ids']} Team.
                                    %else:
                                        Work From Home option has been facilitated to the following employees.
                                    % endif
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                                <div style="margin-left: 1.2rem;margin-bottom:1em;">
                                    <table border="1" cellspacing="2" cellpadding="5" style="border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid #ddd;">
